00:03:20.283 --> 00:03:21.826
Well, I said,

00:03:23.203 --> 00:03:24.370
"I like you."

00:03:25.205 --> 00:03:28.374
I see. You two are quite simple.

00:03:28.458 --> 00:03:31.669
What? Then what do you say
to the person you like?

00:03:31.753 --> 00:03:33.713
I've never done that before.

00:03:33.796 --> 00:03:34.964
