00:10:06.022 --> 00:10:07.023
Kazehaya.

00:10:08.274 --> 00:10:10.234
About Christmas this year…

00:10:10.318 --> 00:10:12.987
Mmm. Yeah, uh, let's get together.

00:10:14.322 --> 00:10:15.156
Mmm.

00:10:15.239 --> 00:10:16.324
With everyone.

00:10:19.410 --> 00:10:20.494
