I'll be the one coordinating.

00:10:27.084 --> 00:10:28.669
Mmm, I see.

00:10:36.636 --> 00:10:37.470
Let's go.

00:10:39.597 --> 00:10:40.514
Mmm.

00:10:51.317 --> 00:10:52.276
