I was the other day?

00:11:05.748 --> 00:11:06.749
Well…

00:11:10.252 --> 00:11:11.504
Are you listening?

00:11:15.257 --> 00:11:16.592
It made me happy.

00:11:18.219 --> 00:11:20.221
You were interested in who I like.

00:11:24.058 --> 00:11:25.184
It made me happy.

00:11:40.282 --> 00:11:41.575
You're the only one

00:11:42.618 --> 00:11:43.703
I've ever loved.

00:11:48.916 --> 00:11:49.834
Just…

00:11:51.419 --> 00:11:52.253
you.

