00:12:18.529 --> 00:12:19.488
Kazehaya.

00:12:20.448 --> 00:12:23.659
It's unusual that Chizu is absent.

00:12:23.743 --> 00:12:25.661
I can't get hold of her either.

00:12:25.745 --> 00:12:27.830
Mmm. I wonder if she's home.

00:12:28.539 --> 00:12:29.498
Not sure.

00:12:30.708 --> 00:12:32.918
Shota, can we talk?

00:12:34.378 --> 00:12:35.337
Sure.

00:12:47.308 --> 00:12:48.642
Aren't you hungry?

00:12:49.185 --> 00:12:52.146
Kazehaya? Why are you here?

00:12:52.229 --> 00:12:54.607
Ryu told me to bring this to you.

00:12:55.107 --> 00:12:57.443
Your mom passed it to him this morning.

00:13:01.155 --> 00:13:02.114
Eat up.

00:13:04.450 --> 00:13:07.536
I will!
Why are you always so calm and collected?

00:13:07.620 --> 00:13:10.414
I hope everything is easy-peasy
between you and Sawako!

00:13:11.707 --> 00:13:14.043
I have my share of troubles.

00:13:23.677 --> 00:13:26.472
It's… so good!

00:13:29.683 --> 00:13:30.684
Damn it!

00:13:30.768 --> 00:13:33.062
I'm gonna be you when I'm reborn!

00:13:33.604 --> 00:13:35.105
Huh? Why?

00:13:35.189 --> 00:13:37.149
I mean, if I were you, then Ryu…

00:13:39.485 --> 00:13:40.402
What?

00:13:43.239 --> 00:13:44.156
Nothing.

00:13:55.292 --> 00:13:57.962
Did you know Ryu…

00:13:59.880 --> 00:14:02.007
likes me?

00:14:03.008 --> 00:14:03.968
Kind of.

00:14:06.720 --> 00:14:08.806
