a Christmas party tonight, aren't you?

00:15:14.371 --> 00:15:16.206
I'll be on a group blind date with nurses.

00:15:18.667 --> 00:15:21.086
Have a good time, everyone. That's all.

00:15:21.170 --> 00:15:22.212
Stand!

00:15:25.883 --> 00:15:27.009
Bow!

00:15:27.092 --> 00:15:29.136
Bye.

00:15:34.433 --> 00:15:37.311
