00:17:44.063 --> 00:17:44.938
No.

00:17:48.358 --> 00:17:49.234
Okay.

00:17:51.945 --> 00:17:53.030
I'm sorry.

00:17:58.702 --> 00:18:01.622
I need to get my bag, so…

00:18:02.247 --> 00:18:03.665
Okay, bye.

00:18:04.291 --> 00:18:05.125
Bye.

00:18:21.058 --> 00:18:23.143
It's not my imagination.

00:18:23.977 --> 00:18:28.941
It's not me, but him
who's keeping distance.

00:18:33.278 --> 00:18:37.074
Am I the cause of his troubles?

00:18:44.665 --> 00:18:45.499
Yano.

00:18:46.208 --> 00:18:47.251
Can we talk?

00:18:48.502 --> 00:18:49.503
What is it?

00:18:58.178 --> 00:19:00.639
Do you know me? I'm Mogi from Class C.

00:19:02.349 --> 00:19:05.519
We're joining you all
at the karaoke party today.

00:19:07.104 --> 00:19:07.938
Oh.

00:19:09.148 --> 00:19:09.982
And?

00:19:12.651 --> 00:19:15.279
I've been interested in you for a while.

00:19:18.031 --> 00:19:20.701
It's so out of the blue.
I don't understand.

00:19:21.285 --> 00:19:23.537
I never had a chance to talk with you,

00:19:24.329 --> 00:19:26.748
so I didn't have the courage
to bring this up.

00:19:27.374 --> 00:19:31.962
But can we talk a bit alone
at the class party?

