00:19:37.759 --> 00:19:39.469
Uh, I won't give up.

00:19:39.553 --> 00:19:41.013
Can we talk again?

00:19:49.813 --> 00:19:52.733
That was Mogi from Class C, right?

00:19:53.567 --> 00:19:54.568
What happened?

00:19:56.987 --> 00:20:00.032
He confessed he likes me,
but I turned him down.

