Let's talk more.

00:23:16.770 --> 00:23:19.106
-The party's heating up.
-Mmm.

00:23:31.368 --> 00:23:32.536
Hey, Kuronuma.

00:23:33.370 --> 00:23:34.788
Aren't you going in?

00:23:34.871 --> 00:23:37.999
Mr. Arai.
You're here for karaoke too?

00:23:38.083 --> 00:23:39.835
I'm crashing your party.

00:23:39.918 --> 00:23:41.753
Who cares about the nurses!

00:23:43.964 --> 00:23:44.798
Huh?

00:23:46.425 --> 00:23:48.969
Is this you thinking about nonsense again?

00:23:50.929 --> 00:23:52.514
It must be about Shota.

00:23:56.518 --> 00:23:57.436
I…

00:23:59.229 --> 00:24:00.439
I'm hopeless.

00:24:01.106 --> 00:24:04.401
I only think about myself.

00:24:05.777 --> 00:24:08.363
I found someone so precious to me.

00:24:09.197 --> 00:24:11.741
I want to know everything about him.

00:24:13.034 --> 00:24:15.912
I want to keep all of him
to myself.

00:24:17.414 --> 00:24:20.584
But it's not possible.

00:24:20.667 --> 00:24:22.127
Mmm.

00:24:23.170 --> 00:24:27.716
Well, if he made you think like that,
I guess he isn't completely useless.

00:24:28.216 --> 00:24:29.217
Useless?

00:24:30.093 --> 00:24:33.972
Don't suppress your feelings,
or you'll end up regretting it.

00:24:34.931 --> 00:24:38.894
Come on.
You have desires and ambitions, don't you?

00:24:40.729 --> 00:24:42.564
Although Shota is stubborn…

00:24:42.647 --> 00:24:43.648
Hmm.

00:24:43.732 --> 00:24:46.818
…wouldn't he understand
if you told him what you really want?

00:24:47.819 --> 00:24:50.739
Your true thoughts
really aren't that much of a big deal,

00:24:50.822 --> 00:24:52.824
so just spit them out.

00:25:01.583 --> 00:25:05.754
If I told him my true thoughts,
would he accept them?

00:25:08.298 --> 00:25:09.382
I'm scared.

00:25:10.509 --> 00:25:13.720
I'm scared, but I want to know

00:25:15.222 --> 00:25:17.682
what he's really thinking too.

00:25:23.188 --> 00:25:26.149
Seriously?
Wait, so she's not really that easy?

00:25:26.233 --> 00:25:28.276
-She may not sleep with me.
-Oh, man.

00:25:28.360 --> 00:25:30.278
-Does it mean that I won the bet?
-No.

00:25:30.362 --> 00:25:31.363
It's not over yet.

00:25:31.446 --> 00:25:33.448
-Huh?
-I'll try again today.

00:25:34.199 --> 00:25:35.033
Oh.

00:25:39.162 --> 00:25:40.455
Uh, hi… hi, Yano.

00:25:40.539 --> 00:25:41.373
Oh.

00:25:41.456 --> 00:25:42.374
Um…

00:25:42.457 --> 00:25:43.875
Uh…

00:25:45.085 --> 00:25:46.211
That's what it was about?

00:25:48.046 --> 00:25:53.510
I heard a rumor
you like that kind of stuff…

00:25:53.593 --> 00:25:55.345
…so I… I wanted to see.

00:25:57.222 --> 00:25:58.598
What the heck?

00:25:59.182 --> 00:26:00.642
You're betting on Ayane?

00:26:01.768 --> 00:26:02.727
Oh, well…

00:26:03.311 --> 00:26:04.521
Oh!

00:26:04.604 --> 00:26:07.107
-Don't mess around with her!
-What's your problem?

00:26:07.190 --> 00:26:09.943
Don't you ever use her
for your stupid bets again!

00:26:12.779 --> 00:26:13.738
Don't!

00:26:18.410 --> 00:26:19.286
Ayane?

00:26:21.580 --> 00:26:24.624
Doing that is pointless.

00:26:45.437 --> 00:26:46.438
Are you okay?

00:26:49.816 --> 00:26:51.359
It's nothing.

00:26:53.778 --> 00:26:55.947
But thank you.

00:26:59.659 --> 00:27:00.910
Of course, right?

00:27:02.579 --> 00:27:05.290
I can only attract jerks like him.

00:27:15.884 --> 00:27:17.594
If you've never loved anyone,

00:27:18.511 --> 00:27:20.180
then you can start with me.

00:27:20.972 --> 00:27:21.931
I mean…

00:27:23.391 --> 00:27:25.310
it doesn't have to be now, of course.

00:27:28.438 --> 00:27:30.565
I'll always cherish you, Ayane.

00:27:52.921 --> 00:27:56.216
-All right, the party's over!
-Huh?

00:27:56.299 --> 00:27:58.635
No after-parties for brats, got it?

00:28:08.436 --> 00:28:09.521
Shall we go?

00:28:10.689 --> 00:28:11.648
Mmm.

00:28:30.333 --> 00:28:33.211
I worry about
if everything suddenly ended.

00:28:34.963 --> 00:28:37.424
But maybe it already has.

00:28:39.008 --> 00:28:41.928
I was so desperate
to be with him last year,

00:28:42.679 --> 00:28:45.515
and it finally happened, but…

00:28:51.062 --> 00:28:56.317
If you ever do that again,
don't be surprised at what happens!

00:29:17.964 --> 00:29:19.549
What's the matter, Kuronuma?

00:29:30.935 --> 00:29:32.020
Liar.

00:29:37.233 --> 00:29:38.526
You're a liar!

00:29:39.486 --> 00:29:41.863
You lied about not having any troubles!

00:29:48.495 --> 00:29:49.913
Today…

00:29:50.622 --> 00:29:51.498
…I just…

00:29:52.999 --> 00:29:54.417
wanted to be with you.

00:29:56.002 --> 00:29:56.836
I know…

00:29:58.630 --> 00:30:03.927
you were doing all this
for the sake of others.

00:30:04.803 --> 00:30:05.887
I know that.

00:30:09.974 --> 00:30:12.435
But I felt lonelier than if I were alone.

00:30:17.816 --> 00:30:19.734
Are you troubled because of me?

00:30:22.821 --> 00:30:25.865
Do you regret about us?

00:30:29.786 --> 00:30:31.120
You…

00:30:33.581 --> 00:30:35.041
don't like me anymore?

00:30:39.546 --> 00:30:43.550
You don't like me being like this?

00:31:13.997 --> 00:31:15.039
I like you.

00:31:17.333 --> 00:31:18.334
I love you.

00:31:45.153 --> 00:31:47.697
Finally, you're looking at me.